{"tid":1055248,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發現《經濟學人》寸中共寸得好應","createTime":"2019-03-10T12:19:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T12:19:41.000Z","uid":241594,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1406f546628aaae5e5b9f7bf1cba1221c2e93fa7","tid":1055248,"uid":241594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T12:19:41.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇到《經濟學人》呢篇文，寸中共寸得好mean<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.economist.com/china/2019/03/09/china-recruits-westerners-to-sell-its-democracy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.economist.com%2Fchina%2F2019%2F03%2F09%2Fchina-recruits-westerners-to-sell-its-democracy&d=NaAPOzxPFgptGlwmNixMN%2FcKxKGkGiqypQ%2FDN8PQntA%3D&h=dee51b3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.economist.com/china/2019/03/09/china-recruits-westerners-to-sell-its-democracy</a> <br />\n<br />\n手痕譯左幾段做中文，反應好繼續譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中共請鬼佬推銷&quot;民主&quot; <br />\n<br />\n每年一度既人大會議（養尊處優既太監議會），為外國記者帶黎幾大挑戰。雖然大人既委員會或者會提出改例或者立新例，有啲又會充當外交角色同外國議員打交道，但三千零個代表既會大部分都好Ｌ悶。其實，人大從來冇否決過共產黨大佬既提議。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20070317/large/17la5p98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20070317%2Flarge%2F17la5p98.jpg&h=370312c5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n參唔參加一年一度既宣傳show真係一個難題。外國記者係記者會會有張櫈坐下既，又會被要求事先交問題(得好少會真係拎黎問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，等國家媒體可以向同胞show下外國記者舉手發問，爭住要參與偽代議民主。 <br />\n<br />\n＂兩會＂期間，北京好冇安全感。(兩會即係人大同政協會議，而後者係一個諮詢架構，安插左生意佬、學者、體育明星。)網絡警察破壞vpn服務，等人翻唔到牆。對於外國記者黎講，兩會大龍鳳通常包括估下可唔可以上網交到故仔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/twapple/640pix/20180305/LN06/LN06_005.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2Ftwapple%2F640pix%2F20180305%2FLN06%2FLN06_005.jpg&h=178e3cb5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後，外國記者會撞到supposed 係同行，但其實唔L識既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢啲人係國家媒體或者中共文宣機器請返黎既外國人。佢地有啲會問預先定好既問題，有啲會讚揚中國既政治制度。中國官方喉告新華今年整左條片叫＂美國人眼中既中國民主＂，片入面一國芝加哥後生仔Colin Linneweber係天安門廣場散住步話 ＂係人都知，民主體制係中國成功既關鍵＂，跟住又吹奏中國既穩定性。之後，佢拎人大代表既mini-profile出黎，當中有農夫、民工同郵差，而佢地既救國建議最終變成法律。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n對呢啲西方人都幾易火滾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中國人自己如果係 天安門廣場讚頌民主，轉手就會俾人拉左。中國既一黨專政唔單止冇真選舉同出版自由呢，仲要求維穩單位不眠不休咁用盡跟蹤、恐嚇、監禁既手段打擊異見者。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/03/10/Qn4hvK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F03%2F10%2FQn4hvK.png&h=c7803b25&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}